# Public Vite variables only — never put secrets here.
#
# Full matrix (Functions + Vite + semantics): docs/portal/ENV_CONTRACT.md
#
# Default local dev: optional CHOKIDAR_USEPOLLING=true (see AGENTS.md).
#
# Portal + API locally: copy .env.portal.local.example → .env.portal.local
#   (Vite --mode portal). API: apps/api/local.settings.json.example → local.settings.json.
#
# Optional: notifications poll interval in milliseconds.
# Min 10000 (10s), max 300000 (5m), default 60000 (60s).
# VITE_NOTIFICATIONS_POLL_MS=60000
